This module allows you to manage the contracts and recurring invoices/bills related to the properties.

.. IMPORTANT::
   This is an alpha version, the data model and design can change at any time without warning.
   Only for development or testing purpose, do not use in production.
   `More details on development status <https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status>`_

Configuration
=============

* Go to Properties > Configuration > Settings.

Usage
=====

To use this module, please read the complete user guide at `<roomdoo.com>`_.

Bug Tracker
===========

Bugs are tracked on `GitHub Issues <https://github.com/OCA/pms/issues>`_.
In case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.
If you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed
`feedback <https://github.com/OCA/pms/issues/new?body=module:%20pms_contract%0Aversion:%2014.0-pms_base%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**>`_.
